prodNameE: Immuno Concepts RELISA ENA Multiparameter Antibody Screening Test System
ingredientsDesc:
ENA Antigen Coated Microwell strips: 3 wellsx12 strips
Sample diluent
Enzyme antibody reagent-Human IgG heavy and light chain specific: 6 mL, Goat antihuman IgG(H&L)conjugated to horseradish peroxidase(HRP). 
Substrate solution: 6 mL,HRP-specific enzyme substrate solution, containing stabilized. 
3,3’,5,5’-tetramethylbenzidine(TMB) and hydrogen peroxide(H2O2).

Stopping reagent: 6 mL, hydrochloric and sulfuric acid (<3%).\npositive control: 1 mL, human positive control serum that contains antibodies to Sm, RNP, SSA/Ro, SSB/La, Scl-70, and Jo-1 antigens. contains 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative.\nnegative control: 1 mL, human negaitive control serum that does not contain antibodies to Sm, RNP, SSA/Ro, SSB/La, Scl-70, and Jo-1 antigens. contains 0.1% sodium azide azide as a preservative.
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區敬業一路１６０號７樓
efficacy: 偵測可萃取核抗原(extractable nuclear antigens, ENA)人體血漿中對抗Sm(Smith)、RNP、SS-A(ro)、SS-B(La)、Scl-70與Jo-1的抗體。
